    "data": [
        {
            "title": "荔枝角物流公司兩職員口角 一男遭同事割傷額頭 疑兇在逃",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"荔枝角物流公司兩職員口角 一男遭同事割傷額頭 疑兇在逃\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0d235aaa43ff419ceeea52da7b8c91cd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250322/_2025032217453343146.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">荔枝角物流公司兩職員口角 一男遭同事割傷額頭 疑兇在逃</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>荔枝角達洋路近迴旋處一間物流公司，今日（22日）下午2時許發生懷疑持刀傷人案。兩名公司職員懷疑因工作問題爭執，期間39歲姓林男子，遭持刀男同事割傷。傷者其後報案求助，警方趕至時行兇男同事則已不知所終。男子額頭中刀但清醒，救護員到場後將他瑪嘉烈醫院救治。警方正追查疑犯下落。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152739/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"39歲姓林男工，遭持刀男同事割傷頭部送院。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da4e4dc673cc7605494f3bf3b6b5b386/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250322_172338837_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        39歲姓林男工，遭持刀男同事割傷頭部送院。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152740/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為荔枝角達洋路近迴旋處一間物流公司。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fc326cbe715da4029fd4d013526e14c9/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250322_172323674.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為荔枝角達洋路近迴旋處一間物流公司。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059682/即時-港聞-荔枝角物流公司兩職員口角-一男遭同事割傷額頭-疑兇在逃",
