            "title": "Coldplay演唱會 ｜門票印錯資料 大批苦主「小紅書」呻要到港換飛  倡Ｃityline 包郵寄新門票",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Coldplay演唱會印錯票，需到港換票。小紅書擷圖\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a3186ac02e655bde68102bd4b62fc9d0/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250322/_2025032217152924691.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Coldplay演唱會印錯票，需到港換票。小紅書擷圖</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【Coldplay/Cityline/啟德體育園/演唱會】英國樂隊Coldplay將於4月8日至12日在啟德主場館舉行巡迴演唱會，實體票已於上周起開放領取，惟近日有網民在小紅書反映收到Cityline要求換票的通知，指「門票上打印的信息有誤」，需帶現有門票到香港7個指定地點換領新門票，否則無法入場。內地網友對換票措施及沒有賠償表示不滿，認為需專程到港換票因路程遠、額外承擔交通費用十分不便，更有大批網民湧入文化體育及旅遊局局長羅淑佩「小紅書」個人主頁投訴事件。\n\n</p><h2>實體門票印錯信息</h2>\n<p>不少內地網民在「小紅書」控訴收到Cityline或Klook的電郵通知，指「門票上的資料出現偏差」，要求其於3月24日至4月7日期間，到香港7個指定地點更換門票，現時持有門票將作廢。相關網民對比門票後發現，1,399價位的普通門票右下方疑被印錯「VIP-FLORIS」，惟正確門票應印為「KLOOK Hirer」、「STAN VISA」或「STAN MAST」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"有網民在社媒反映收到Cityline要求換票的通知。小紅書擷圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/24e52878e6c6edd33ef89475c0174617/2025-03/_20250322163229.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有網民在社媒反映收到Cityline要求換票的通知。小紅書擷圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"郵件指「門票上打印的信息有誤」。小紅書擷圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/27cfa6b2755b01ddafe37ebe0d4bf44e/2025-03/_20250322163225.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        郵件指「門票上打印的信息有誤」。小紅書擷圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"不少內地網民在小紅書控訴收到Cityline或Klook的電郵通知。小紅書擷圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4d3f7acfcaf28f6b021ac93a0324155e/2025-03/_20250322163601.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        不少內地網民在小紅書控訴收到Cityline或Klook的電郵通知。小紅書擷圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"需更換門票的內地網民更紛紛湧入羅淑佩小紅書個人主頁發表投訴評論。小紅書擷圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1d4112ea54e3361a30d77a90c2fd42b3/2025-03/_20250322163558.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        需更換門票的內地網民更紛紛湧入羅淑佩小紅書個人主頁發表投訴評論。小紅書擷圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"批網民湧入羅淑佩小紅書個人主頁投訴該事件。小紅書擷圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8966ebf0415f0e2731d8d2a14b634fc7/2025-03/_20250322163553.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        批網民湧入羅淑佩小紅書個人主頁投訴該事件。小紅書擷圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"1,399價位的普通門票右下方疑被印錯「VIP-FLORIS」。小紅書圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/10bc7d6c97b304b281c06e960a4633b6/2025-03/_20250322164224.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        1,399價位的普通門票右下方疑被印錯「VIP-FLORIS」。小紅書圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"正確門票應印為「STAN VISA」或「STAN MAST」。小紅書圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4de09c155c47b92acaf08cefad5aa538/2025-03/_20250322164104.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        正確門票應印為「STAN VISA」或「STAN MAST」。小紅書圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"正確門票應印為「STAN VISA」或「STAN MAST」。小紅書圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a64fb0ea5c4899cad38a171b678e209a/2025-03/_20250322164100.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        正確門票應印為「STAN VISA」或「STAN MAST」。小紅書圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>網民湧羅淑佩專頁投訴 建議Cityline包郵寄新門票</h2>\n<p>需更換門票的內地網民更紛紛湧入羅淑佩「小紅書」個人主頁留言投訴，質疑Cityline補救方式不合理，未從消費者角度出發，指換票時效性與地域限制加大時間和交通成本，亦對換票必要性提出疑慮。他們希望Cityline就本次事件公開道歉，並承諾改進票務管理流程。\n\n</p>\n<p>有網民建議Cityline免費將新門票郵寄至消費者指定地址，亦有人建議Cityline更新系統識別，網民無需換票，或若上述方案均無法執行，應向消費者賠償。許多涉事網民亦指已向Cityline寄投訴電郵，惟未有回覆。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059675/即時-港聞-Coldplay演唱會-門票印錯資料-大批苦主-小紅書-呻要到港換飛-倡Ｃityline-包郵寄新門票",
